Package: smerc
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Methods for Regional Counts
Version: 0.4.2
Date: 2018-04-07
Author: Joshua French
Maintainer: Joshua French <joshua.french@ucdenver.edu>
Description: Implements several statistical methods for 
analyzing areal count data, with a focus on the 
detection of spatial clusters or clustering.
